1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 6=

21
00:01:26,150 --> 00:01:27,280
It was much calmer

22
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:29,480
these past nights.

23
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,680
Still a little bloating,

24
00:01:33,310 --> 00:01:35,070
but the pain's mild.

25
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,790
I noticed

26
00:01:36,950 --> 00:01:38,920
your complexion has returned.

27
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,640
The dark circles are gone too.

28
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:44,070
That herbal steaming works.

29
00:01:44,870 --> 00:01:45,920
Didn't expect

30
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,040
Ye Jin's

31
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:49,400
actually skilled.

32
00:01:50,550 --> 00:01:51,400
Biqing.

33
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:52,250
Yes, Your Grace.

34
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:55,760
Pick five bolts of fine silk.

35
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,710
Since she has talent,

36
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,350
I should show her some respect.

37
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,640
Have her come for a follow-up.

38
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:04,760
Be polite.

39
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,280
Understood.

40
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,080
With such a generous reward,

41
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,590
she'll surely be grateful.

42
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:21,310
I'm getting so bloated.

43
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,430
My face's gotten so puffy

44
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,840
that my makeup's a mess.

45
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:27,960
Your Grace, you're glowing.

46
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,870
A bit plump

47
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,240
is a blessing.

48
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:34,280
His Majesty can't stand that.

49
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,310
If I get any bigger,

50
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:38,710
he might

51
00:02:38,710 --> 00:02:40,590
never visit me again.

52
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,710
Does you

53
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:44,150
remember Ye Jin

54
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:45,630
from the Empress Dowager's palace?

55
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:49,030
The one who helped you last time?

56
00:02:52,590 --> 00:02:53,960
Of course I remember.

57
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:56,870
She's skilled in medicine.

58
00:02:56,870 --> 00:02:58,240
Especially diet therapy.

59
00:02:58,710 --> 00:02:59,560
Yesterday,

60
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,870
I went with you
to greet the Empress Dowager.

61
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,960
Her Highness looks much improved.

62
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,240
Must be her doing.

63
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:07,870
Why don't I

64
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:10,310
go invite her over?

65
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:11,310
Maybe

66
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:12,910
she can solve your problem.

67
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:14,840
Fine.

68
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,630
Zhen'er,

69
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,120
go to the storehouse

70
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,630
and get five bolts of silk,

71
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,120
a set of pearl hairpins,

72
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,190
and write a letter.

73
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:26,590
Thank her

74
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:28,470
for helping me last time

75
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:29,630
and ask her

76
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,280
to come

77
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,870
for a chat.

78
00:03:33,430 --> 00:03:34,270
Yes.

79
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,590
I'm on it.

80
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,710
- Miss Ye Jin.
- Miss Ye Jin.

81
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:57,680
First come, first served.

82
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:59,030
Don't compete with me today.

83
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,000
(Consort Lan)

84
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:01,270
(Consort Duan)

85
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,710
In this palace,

86
00:04:03,190 --> 00:04:04,400
there's no such rule.

87
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,590
It's about influence.

88
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:06,590
Consort Duan said

89
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:07,870
these are only a small token.

90
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:08,750
There will be more.

91
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,430
Consort Lan has rewards as well.

92
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:11,520
They're even better.

93
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,360
Everyone knows

94
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:13,800
my lady is the most generous.

95
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:16,240
Money talks.

96
00:04:17,940 --> 00:04:18,800
Enough.

97
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,360
(They're both dangerous.)

98
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:22,120
(Choosing either is trouble.)

99
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,430
I am deeply honored

100
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:24,800
and truly overwhelmed.

101
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:27,390
I should go immediately
when summoned,

102
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:30,510
but I simply

103
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,680
don't have time today.

104
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:35,040
Because the 14th Prince

105
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,120
ordered an herbal bath.

106
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:39,000
If I'm late,

107
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,920
my life is forfeit.

108
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:42,680
But I know

109
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,920
both consorts' conditions.

110
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,510
Here are two prescriptions.

111
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:46,510
Take one each

112
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:47,800
and report back.

113
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,310
I can't accept rewards

114
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,070
without merit.

115
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:55,480
If they work,

116
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:57,190
reward me later.

117
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:09,800
Your Highness,
she used you as a shield.

118
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,630
Used me?

119
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,680
She's bold.

120
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,560
Exactly.

121
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,390
That woman is out of control.

122
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:22,160
Mentioning a bath in broad daylight?

123
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,800
She's just stirring things up

124
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,000
and causing rumors.

125
00:05:25,390 --> 00:05:27,190
She's using your name to get her way

126
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:28,630
and ruining your reputation.

127
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:30,070
She deserves to die.

128
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:35,270
My reputation isn't great anyway.

129
00:05:35,630 --> 00:05:37,240
Doesn't matter.

130
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,950
What interests me

131
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,000
is her medical skill,

132
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:43,720
the way she talks,

133
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,310
and those strange words

134
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:47,750
she keeps using.

135
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:49,480
It makes me feel like

136
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:52,040
she's no ordinary maid.

137
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:54,800
So you suspect her background?

138
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:57,600
Should we send someone to investigate?

139
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:59,600
Why make such a fuss?

140
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:01,830
Let me

141
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:03,310
test her myself.

142
00:06:04,070 --> 00:06:04,950
It will

143
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,270
be faster

144
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:07,920
and more interesting.

145
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,600
The Emperor has arrived.

146
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:25,750
What's going on here?

147
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:27,480
What's she up to?

148
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:28,750
Your Majesty,

149
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,430
the consort's been unwell.

150
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:32,050
Ye Jin from
the Empress Dowager's palace

151
00:06:32,050 --> 00:06:33,240
has prescribed

152
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,920
herbal steaming.

153
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,920
It works well,

154
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:38,240
so she uses it daily.

155
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,080
Absurd.

156
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:18,500
(Twelve Earthly Branches)

157
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,940
Consort Duan.

158
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:32,870
What are you doing?

159
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,880
Your Majesty.

160
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,200
Nonsense.

161
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:39,040
You're pregnant.

162
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,120
How can you be so reckless?

163
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:41,270
What if you

164
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:41,960
hurt the baby?

165
00:07:42,010 --> 00:07:43,070
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

166
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,480
I…

167
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,680
Ye Jin from

168
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,870
the Empress Dowager's palace

169
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,950
taught me this prenatal yoga.

170
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:55,040
She said it stabilizes the pregnancy

171
00:07:55,430 --> 00:07:56,870
and controls my weight.

172
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,630
I've tried it for two days,

173
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:00,160
and my back no longer aches.

174
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:01,660
Even my breathing
feels smooth now.

175
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:03,800
I feel so light.

176
00:08:04,430 --> 00:08:05,600
Ye Jin again?

177
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,480
Who is this woman?

178
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:20,830
Greetings, Your Majesty.

179
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,270
What time is it?

180
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,800
Mother hasn't taken her medicine?

181
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:26,120
Your Majesty.

182
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:27,920
Since the day before yesterday,

183
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,480
Her Highness has
refused my prescriptions.

184
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:32,870
I've been waiting here

185
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,790
to advise her,

186
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:37,670
but she refuses to listen.

187
00:08:38,450 --> 00:08:39,510
Is the medicine too bitter?

188
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:41,360
Not at all.

189
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:43,270
According to the servants,

190
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,790
she trusts a maid

191
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,320
named Ye Jin.

192
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:50,240
Claims her ancestors
were imperial physicians.

193
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:51,480
She scrapped

194
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:53,200
my prescriptions,

195
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:57,600
replaced them with sugar-free soups,

196
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:02,200
and some

197
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:05,270
waist-twisting exercise.

198
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:06,840
Exercise?

199
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:07,990
Yes.

200
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,960
The Empress Dowager says

201
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:13,390
it improves her appetite

202
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:16,790
and keeps her hands and feet warm.

203
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:20,030
I think it's just a gimmick

204
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:21,390
with no medical basis.

205
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:22,790
How did someone like that

206
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,390
even enter Cining Palace?

207
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:26,870
I heard

208
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:31,390
the 14th Prince recommended her.

209
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,240
Since you're here,

210
00:09:42,150 --> 00:09:43,240
come in.

211
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,390
Greetings, Your Highness.

212
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:52,150
You used to doubt my methods.

213
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:56,360
Why did you
ask for acupuncture today?

214
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,750
Your treatment

215
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,440
works somehow.

216
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:03,150
I sleep better.

217
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:05,230
Great.

218
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,750
Let's get started.

219
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,200
What are you doing?

220
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:28,080
Greetings, Your Majesty.

221
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,040
Brother.

222
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,320
Acupuncture.

223
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,040
Impudent maid.

224
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,600
How dare you needle a prince?

225
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:34,870
What if something

226
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:35,870
goes wrong?

227
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,440
Don't blame her, Brother.

228
00:10:37,790 --> 00:10:40,000
I asked her to do it.

229
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,630
I haven't

230
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,390
slept well lately

231
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,600
and nothing worked.

232
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,390
She claimed she could help.

233
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:49,000
So I let her try.

234
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,840
Ridiculous.

235
00:10:50,670 --> 00:10:51,840
A mere maid

236
00:10:52,270 --> 00:10:53,630
claiming medicine?

237
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:55,990
Brother,

238
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:58,510
she's no ordinary maid.

239
00:10:58,630 --> 00:11:01,240
Her skills are extraordinary.

240
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,630
Since eating

241
00:11:02,630 --> 00:11:04,270
her sugar-free snacks,

242
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,550
Mother has improved.

243
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,840
She isn't startled
at night anymore.

244
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:12,080
I thought her methods

245
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,790
were worth trying.

246
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,280
It seems

247
00:11:16,550 --> 00:11:18,510
you're bewitched too.

248
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:21,120
A suspect in a murder case.

249
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:23,360
What spell did she cast on you?

250
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:25,870
You released her

251
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,080
and placed her in Cining Palace.

252
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:30,150
I won't allow this.

253
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,440
Guards.

254
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,960
Your Majesty.

255
00:11:36,270 --> 00:11:37,320
Maid Ye Jin

256
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,390
has deceived her masters

257
00:11:38,390 --> 00:11:39,380
and interfered.

258
00:11:39,430 --> 00:11:40,870
She delayed her treatment.

259
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:42,030
This is a grave crime.

260
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,780
Send her to the labor camp immediately

261
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,320
as a low-ranking servant.

262
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,440
Let this be a warning.

263
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:48,600
Your Majesty, I'm innocent.

264
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,270
Prince, help me.

265
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,600
Since you've decided,

266
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:55,960
I have no objections.

267
00:11:56,370 --> 00:11:57,230
Take her.

268
00:11:57,270 --> 00:11:58,110
Wait.

269
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,200
Your Highness.

270
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,600
Help me.

271
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,750
You jerk.

272
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:11,060
♪I am but an outsider♪

273
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:13,260
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

274
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:17,540
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

275
00:12:17,540 --> 00:12:21,780
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

276
00:12:26,060 --> 00:12:29,300
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

277
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:32,860
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

278
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:35,380
♪I know how this story ends♪

279
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:39,940
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

280
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:44,380
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

281
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:52,660
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

282
00:12:52,660 --> 00:12:55,940
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

283
00:12:56,140 --> 00:12:59,220
♪A history that no one can search♪

284
00:12:59,460 --> 00:13:02,740
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

285
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:04,540
♪I am but an outsider♪

286
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:06,780
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

287
00:13:06,780 --> 00:13:10,820
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

288
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:15,500
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

289
00:13:19,420 --> 00:13:22,820
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

290
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:26,180
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

291
00:13:26,180 --> 00:13:28,660
♪I know how this story ends♪

292
00:13:28,660 --> 00:13:32,820
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

293
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:36,100
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

294
00:13:36,100 --> 00:13:39,900
♪Please forget me and move on♪

